title: How To Make Lasagna For Two from Don Angie
description:
Married couple and co-owners of Don Angie in Manhattan's West Village, Angie Rito and Scott Tacinelli, make lasagna for two in the Munchies Test Kitchen. This rolled lasagna, which is Don Angie’s most popular dish, includes a homemade pasta dough, béchamel sauce, Bolognese sauce, and parmesan and mozzarella cheeses.
